| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5326 — Recovery Inhibition (obscura)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1df5220d-1158-5733-abc9-913ca6ef59c5"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
